pt.davidafsilva.jtrakt.model.tv

Class TvShowSeason

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.davidafsilva.jtrakt.model.common.BaseModel
      • pt.davidafsilva.jtrakt.model.tv.TvShowSeason

  • public final class TvShowSeason
extends BaseModel

    This class represents a TV show season.

    It's the result of deserializing: 
     {
   "season": 1,
   "episodes": 8,
   "url": "http://trakt.tv/show/silicon-valley/season/1",
   "poster": "http://slurm.trakt.us/images/seasons/23332-1.16.jpg",
   "images": {
     "poster": "http://slurm.trakt.us/images/seasons/23332-1.16.jpg"
   }
 }
    Author:
    David Silva
